This Power BI report delivers a thorough analysis of retail sales, incorporating metrics such as total sales, sales by category, and performance by region. 
The interactive dashboards visualize trends over time, seasonal variations, and sales patterns across different periods. 
Detailed KPIs, including average transaction value, sales growth, and customer demographics, are presented to offer a clear view of business performance. 
The report also provides comparative analysis of various sales channels and highlights high-performing products and regions. 
By integrating data from multiple sources, it enables users to uncover actionable insights, optimize inventory management, tailor marketing efforts, and drive strategic decision-making to enhance sales performance and operational efficiency.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In this Power BI report, custom KPIs are included to track annual loss and profit,providing a clear view of yearly financial performance. 
Additionally, metrics are integrated to display Month-to-Date (MTD), Year-to-Date (YTD), and Quarter-to-Date (QTD) figures for each year, 
along with comparative analysis to the previous yearâ€™s MTD, YTD, and QTD. This setup enables a detailed performance assessment, 
helping stakeholders identify trends, evaluate progress, and make informed decisions based on comprehensive financial and operational data.
